# ************* SauceDemo Task *******************#


Useing Seleniun webdriver framework I managed to write automation code to simulate a user checking out a product through SauceDemo website.


# Tech:

- Java 
- Maven 
- TestNG 
- DDT
- POM Design Pattern





# Used ConfigProperties class to read from Configdata property file



# Requirements:


*Eclips(install Testng from marketPlace)
*JDK15
*let POM file install the dependencies


# Steps:


*Clone the project 
*We have two ways to run the project
1-open testng, click right and run.
2-Run using cmd
 2.1-open cmd 
 2.2-open project directoy (using cd "project path")
 2.3-Type mvn clean install





